name: Sakurajima Mai (Bunny Girl anime)
description:
Lora model of Sakurajima Mai from Seishun Buta Yarou wa Bunny Girl Senpai no Yume o Minai anime. Previews made with weight 0.9-1.0.

A request from friend, luckily came out pretty well on first try :) Also first time was tagging completely manually and looks like it worked out (through I had some problems with leg on the bed picture, so maybe some poses can have some issues).

School uniform - sakurajima mai, hairclip, rabbit hair ornament, brown jacket, white shirt, red necktie, sweater vest, blue skirt, black pantyhose, loafers

Bunny girl - sakurajima mai, rabbit ears, black hairband, hairclip, rabbit hair ornament, detached collar, black bowtie, black leotard, wrist cuffs, rabbit tail, black pantyhose, high heels
